#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.extract.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.extract"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.extract:1 of
msgid ""
"Extract structured information from text content in a series using a "
"language model."
msgstr "使用语言模型从系列中的文本内容提取结构化信息。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.extract of
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "参数"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.extract:3 of
msgid ""
"A maxframe Series containing text data to extract information from. Each "
"element should be a text string."
msgstr "一个包含待提取信息文本数据的 maxframe Series。每个元素应为一个文本字符串。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.extract:6 of
msgid "Language model instance used for information extraction."
msgstr "用于信息提取的语言模型实例。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.extract:8 of
msgid ""
"Schema definition for the extraction. Can be a dictionary defining the "
"structure or a Pydantic BaseModel class that will be converted to JSON "
"schema."
msgstr ""
"提取的模式定义。可以是定义结构的字典，或会被转换为 JSON 模式的 Pydantic "
"BaseModel 类。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.extract:11 of
msgid ""
"Description of the extraction task to help the model understand what to "
"extract."
msgstr "提取任务的描述，以帮助模型理解需要提取的内容。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.extract:13 of
msgid ""
"Examples of the extraction task in format [(input_text, expected_output),"
" ...], to help LLM better understand the extraction requirements."
msgstr ""
"提取任务的示例，格式为 [(input_text, expected_output), ...]，以帮助大语言"
"模型更好地理解提取需求。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.extract:16 of
msgid "Index for the output series, by default None, will generate new index."
msgstr "输出序列的索引，默认为 None，将生成新索引。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.extract of
msgid "Returns"
msgstr "返回"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.extract:19 of
msgid ""
"A DataFrame containing the extracted information and success status. "
"Columns include 'output' (extracted structured data) and 'success' "
"(boolean status). If 'success' is False, the 'output' column will contain"
" error information instead of the expected output."
msgstr ""
"一个包含提取信息和成功状态的 DataFrame。列包括 'output'（提取的结构化数据"
"）和 'success'（布尔状态）。如果 'success' 为 False，则 'output' 列将包含"
"错误信息而非预期输出。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.extract:25 of
msgid "Examples"
msgstr "示例"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.extract:55 of
msgid "Notes"
msgstr "备注"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.extract:56 of
msgid ""
"**Preview:** This API is in preview state and may be unstable. The "
"interface may change in future releases."
msgstr ""
"**预览：** 此 API 处于预览状态，可能不稳定。接口可能在未来的版本中"
"发生变化。"

